{
  "stem": "4361.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in fact, my older brother, Mano, who was a wonderful influence on my life and who was regarded with a great deal of respect because-- by my parents and so he sort of assured me, don't worry, Baba.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the time comes, I'll interfere and intervene, and you will go to your law school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, things didn't turn out quite that way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] She must have been because she was a wonderful mother and grandmother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remembered that my mother and her brother would more or less fight over her with whom she should stay.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is how much beloved she was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she would stay six months with us-- that's-- these are my memories of her-- and six months in my uncle's house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in those six months, my mother and father would visit her practically every evening.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she must have been a good person.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a very active Jewish life in my days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I say in my days, I'm, I'm beginning with the Romanian occupation-- well, I shouldn't say occupation-- but the Romanian regime, because the Trianon Treaty during the First World War awarded the entire Transylvania to Romania.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And while my parents were born there, and my grandparents and so was I, we were switching governments.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I was born under Romanian government, but ultimately, it was the Hungarian government who did what it did to us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Through the Nazis, I should add.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But going back to the Jewish life, it was a good, strong Jewish life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In fact, I remember it was idealistic in the sense that the youth was idealistic.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We belonged-- most of my friends, including me-- belonged to Zionist groups.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I belonged to the junior Zionist group called Habonim.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
